wmsLayer.title: GA0336 5 2m
wmsLayer.description: This layer is tile 5 of a bathymetric grid collected on marine survey GA0336, over the Petrel Sub-basin, offshore Northern Australia. The total dataset consists of 11 tiles gridded at two metre resolution. The colour ramp for the WMS is stretched between 40-115 metres water depth. The dataset can be downloaded at the following URL http://services.ga.gov.au/metadata-gateway/metadata/record/75120.
